---
const footerLinks = [
  { href: '/', label: '首页' },
  { href: '/tech', label: '认识技术' },
  { href: '/impact', label: '积极影响' },
  { href: '/use-well', label: '善用技术' },
  { href: '/resources', label: '资源入口' },
  { href: '/about', label: '关于' },
];
---

<footer class="site-footer" role="contentinfo">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <h3>Silicon Age｜硅基时代</h3>
      <p>非营利公益网站<br />关注人工智能、信息化与具身智能的积极作用</p>
    </div>
    <nav class="footer-col" aria-label="页脚导航">
      <h4>页面</h4>
      {footerLinks.map(link => (
        <a href={link.href}>{link.label}</a>
      ))}
    </nav>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <p>本站内容仅用于公益传播和一般科普，不构成专业建议。</p>
  </div>
</footer>
